<main>
  <section class="p-0">
    <%= render "home/carrossel" %>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">Fotos do Ultimo ORAR</h2>
      </div>

      <% galeria_imagens = [
        ["ulisses.jpeg", "Ulisses"],
        ["candeias.jpeg", "Candeias"],
        ["setimus.jpeg", "Setimus"],
        ["forjados.jpeg", "Forjados"],
        ["volei.jpeg", "Volei"],
        ["eldorado.jpeg", "Eldorado"]
      ] %>

      <div class="row g-4">
        <% galeria_imagens.each do |image, alt_text| %>
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="orar-galeria-card shadow-sm rounded-3">
              <%= responsive_asset_picture(
                image,
                alt: alt_text,
                sizes: "(min-width: 992px) 33vw, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw",
                width: 7008,
                height: 4672,
                picture_class: "orar-galeria-midia",
                img_class: "orar-galeria-imagem",
                aspect_ratio: "4 / 3"
              ) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <h2 class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <span aria-hidden="true">
          <i class="bi bi-chat-dots-fill"></i>
        </span>
        Perguntas Frequentes
      </h2>

      <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center orar-faq-grid">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-10">
                  <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary mb-0">1. O que e o ORAR?</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="col-2 text-end">
                  <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p class="text-secondary mt-3 mb-0">
                  As olimpiadas regionais Adventistas de Rondonia, <strong>ORAR</strong>, sao iniciativas do ministerio jovem para promover evolucao fisica, mental e espiritual dos jovens. O objetivo e proporcionar um ambiente saudavel e estimulante para o desenvolvimento integral dos participantes, fortalecendo a integracao entre as regioes do estado.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-10">
                  <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary mb-0">2. Quem pode participar?</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="col-2 text-end">
                  <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul class="text-secondary mt-3 mb-0">
                  <li>Todos aqueles que frequentam regularmente uma sociedade jovem.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-10">
                  <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary mb-0">3. Quando e onde vai ser o ORAR 2026?</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="col-2 text-end">
                  <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul class="text-secondary mt-3 mb-0">
                  <li>O ORAR 2026 sera realizado no IFRO (Instituto Federal de Rondonia), no periodo de [Data Inicio] a [Data Fim].</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      function toggleAnswer(card) {
        const answer = card.querySelector(".faq-answer");
        const icon = card.querySelector("i");

        answer.classList.toggle("active");

        if (answer.classList.contains("active")) {
          icon.classList.remove("bi-plus-lg");
          icon.classList.add("bi-dash-lg");
        } else {
          icon.classList.remove("bi-dash-lg");
          icon.classList.add("bi-plus-lg");
        }
      }
    </script>

    <style>
      .orar-galeria-card {
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #f8f9fa;
      }

      .orar-galeria-midia {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .orar-galeria-imagem {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: center;
      }

      .faq-card {
        cursor: pointer;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .faq-card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .faq-answer {
        max-height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out;
      }

      .faq-answer.active {
        max-height: 220px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .faq-card h5 {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .faq-card i {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </section>
</main>
